Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie! I had those two set this whole thing up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just really wanted to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I didn't have a chance to talk to you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you don't like these sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But would you please consider hanging out with me some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please give me a chance and go out with me for just one month?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try going out with her for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, it looks like I really couldn't fall for you. Sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been much better to decline at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go out with some girl you don't even like. You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:14.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:20.76,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:32.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:40.24,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:44.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:50.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:59.76,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:04.68,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:11.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:18.57,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:14.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:20.76,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:32.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:40.24,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:44.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:50.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:59.76,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:04.68,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:11.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:18.57,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:34.09,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,960)\pos(160,381)\fscx112.5\fscy103.75}Episode 21 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.21,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sleep over on Sunday night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some sort of joke...? I'm a little shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are going to a wedding in Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, you said you wanted to go somewhere we could be alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a trip, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought we could be together all day, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the afternoon, we can see a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come early evening, we can happily return home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For dinner, we'd have spaghetti carbonara. I made it last week, so I won't make any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom will call sometime during the night and I'll answer like I always do. No problem there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I already cleaned the bath, making it nice and sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should cover my fun and exciting weekend plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while gazing up at the starry sky, we can have fun talking all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I doubt all of that will happen... for a boy and girl only seventeen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird seeing him way out at this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano! What'd you come out this way to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.59,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Condoms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully... getting this doesn't mean too much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to hold Takahashi in my arms till morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold her tight in my arms... kiss her... and then hug her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight through till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Takahashi sleeps in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pajamas, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if they had spaghetti straps like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope tomorrow comes soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's skipping...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You headed to the station? Meeting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard some eyewitness information that you went to a certain store last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but someone you knew found you in the next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a dork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information really travels fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strangely pretty open with his feelings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
