Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to get on the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the bus just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but if this isn't important, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have to get on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And be sure to lock up behind you. I'll call you later tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget your keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:07:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry and get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that this day will become something special...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... she won't wake up, no matter how much I try to wake her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I shake her, she won't wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call for an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in the ICU right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's late... and he's always so punctual, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, mind if I take a quick phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have plans did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah... I kinda had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano? You're already a half hour late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get through your cellphone at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Something pressing came up, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think I'll be tied up for a bit, so could you go home for now, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what about the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time will you be able to get to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto's mom collapsed. I'm with her at the hospital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're not sure... It might have been a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She still hasn't come out of the ICU yet, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds pretty bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, until we know what her condition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... why do you have to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come over here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't abandon her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go home and wait for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takahashi? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going home! Come here right now! I won't go home until you get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahash--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he choose Yamamoto-san over me today... of all days...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I've been talking the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me... do you have any siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a little brother... but... didn't we just talk about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, excuse me for a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely lost it. She's even blocked calls from me and won't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to go back inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you persuade her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to Takahashi right now, you won't have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even realize what you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or well, she does... but he hardly ever comes home because he's always with some other woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her other relatives live far away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has no one to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, her only family is her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can really understand... those uneasy feelings she's having right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do you have to be the one who looks after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for her if you don't give her some half-hearted sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really say that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're doing the same thing as me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going back inside, so... I'll leave contacting her up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something came up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm sorry, but would you mind if I made another phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I won't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter how long you stay there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! I don't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takaha--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone! Takeuchi-kun, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please... leave me alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't Yano... understand my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... don't call me again, even if Yano asks you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being so stubborn for no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't be my normal, happy self...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the girl he was with wasn't Yamamoto-san, I know I wouldn't be this stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what happened, I definitely wanted him to come today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... I don't want to be all alone at a time like this, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then... are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun, you haven't been able to drag your eyes away from that window since that phone call earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're family, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no abnormalities in her brain waves or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the medicine we've administered, her blood pressure is returning to normal levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we caught it early enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This accident most likely occurred from an overload of work and stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she will wake up momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take care of the hospital paperwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to stay here overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll decide that after she wakes up and I see how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed lunch because of this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my treat, so why don't you go get something at the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I... take off for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I really have to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... I'm sorry for pulling you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially on a weekend like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'd really like to be with you until your mom wakes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything happens, don't hesitate to give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything physically, but I can at least be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for today, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to your mom for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me walk you to the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. If you don't hurry up, the cafeteria will close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me at least give you some money for a taxi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the plaza in front of the station. I'm sorry, but please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first snow of the season!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was pretty cold out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing out here! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've worn gloves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! You can see your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take my gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're giving them to me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your friend's girlfriend, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how many times we have the same conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These sorts of things take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you think I'm the worst scum on the face of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bad traffic jam at the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop at the light over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given up on you so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought that would be best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... you're crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mutual love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loving someone else's lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to go home and wait there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long were you planning on standing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he likes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can promise you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...make you cry, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:26.57,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima kimi ga iikaketa kotoba ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:33.08,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yubisaki ni sotto oritekita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:39.71,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo iwanakute ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:45.51,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumaida yubi wo gyutto atatamete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:23:02.02,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba wa kotoba dakara kokoro hanbun mo tsutaenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:15.20,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute yuuyake futari wo tsutsundeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:27.42,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiageru mune no omoi kokoro ga itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:38.68,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshi kimi ga tabibito ni nattara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:45.19,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kore gurai kimi wo matteru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:51.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa kawaru sono tabi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:57.91,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kioku ga usuragu koto ga attemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:13.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka wo konna fuu ni kokoro ippai de aisenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:21.48,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaritai taisetsu na kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:27.40,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsu datte futari wa hitori ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:35.07,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mune ga kawaresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:40.87,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Furete hoshii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.33,0:24:57.14,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute kaerenai kono mama aruiteitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:25:12.45,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yabaisaki ni kanjiteiru kokoro no kotoba wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:26.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The words you were just about to say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:33.08,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,fell softly onto my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:39.71,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:45.51,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clasp your hand tightly and warm it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:23:02.02,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Because words are words, I can't express half of the feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:15.20,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating as the sunset engulfs the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:27.42,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches from all the feelings welling up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:38.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to become a traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:45.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,would I be able to wait for you as I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:51.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As the seasons change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:57.91,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even if our memories are to fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:13.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to love someone with all of my heart like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:21.48,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect the precious you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:27.40,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:35.07,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me heart feels so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:40.87,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.33,0:24:57.14,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating that I can't go home. I want to keep walking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:25:12.45,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the words from your heart on my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.92,0:25:34.94,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\pos(437,377)\fscx103.75\fscy123.75}Episode 22 Preview ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.90,0:25:09.48,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Take... I don't\N understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:12.11,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to\N go out with Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.11,0:25:13.15,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...without hurting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:17.16,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can understand him...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.16,0:25:19.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...a whole lot more than you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:23.33,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust, is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:26.92,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something\N I always seem to be lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.92,0:25:28.79,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to \Nprotect you, Takahashi.
